2
00:01:50,630 --> 00:01:53,380
Gum-Gum... Bazooka!

3
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:58,140
Retreat for now, men!

4
00:01:58,140 --> 00:02:01,140
Everyone! Find any way out you can!

5
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:04,270
– Wait for us!
– Wait for us!

6
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:09,320
Did we all make it?!

7
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:12,610
Are the people you were with
when you got off the ship here?!

8
00:02:12,610 --> 00:02:14,320
Yes!

9
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,490
Yeah.

10
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:16,620
Yes.

11
00:02:16,620 --> 00:02:17,580
Yep!

12
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,700
Captain Buggy isn't...

13
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,910
Captain Buggy isn't here!

14
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,500
Alright!

15
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,260
I've finally finished my flashy raft!

16
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,140
Go!

17
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:38,760
Set sail!

18
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,190
What's with this crap so soon?!

19
00:02:46,650 --> 00:02:49,860
I refuse to lose! Damn you!

20
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,200
I'm gonna eat you!

21
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:12,260
Part-Part Cannon!

22
00:03:19,930 --> 00:03:21,640
Quit struggling!

23
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:23,430
Just accept your fate!

24
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:36,320
Sorry! I'm sorry!

25
00:03:37,410 --> 00:03:40,120
Forgive me!

26
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:53,630
C'mon! C'mon!

27
00:03:54,130 --> 00:03:56,760
My plan is foolproof!

28
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,020
Dummy! Dummy! Dummy!

29
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,650
I caught him!

30
00:04:13,110 --> 00:04:15,030
I'm caught?! Huh?! What?!

31
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,610
How did things turn out this way?!

32
00:04:18,610 --> 00:04:20,780
Stop! Stop! Ow, ow, ow!

33
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:24,200
Is the end here already?!

34
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:24,950
Stop–

35
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:41,260
Where am I now?

36
00:04:43,970 --> 00:04:46,140
Leave this place!

37
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:47,890
Who's there?!

38
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,980
Begone from this island at once
if you value your life!

39
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:57,490
What are these things?

40
00:04:57,490 --> 00:04:59,570
The animals of this forest.

41
00:04:59,570 --> 00:05:02,950
Don't mess with them
unless you want to die!

42
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:03,950
Oh?

43
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:07,370
These animals are
pretty flashy and interesting...

44
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:10,500
I told you not to go any farther!

45
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:13,630
Blast it!

46
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:15,710
He snuck a shot at me!

47
00:05:15,710 --> 00:05:17,420
Damn! I missed!

48
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:19,170
There you are!

49
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:22,220
What is this?!

50
00:05:23,470 --> 00:05:25,010
Gotcha!

51
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,970
Come out!

52
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:27,970
Ow! Ow! Ow!

53
00:05:27,970 --> 00:05:30,810
Dammit! You have a devil fruit ability!

54
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,850
So what if I do?!

55
00:05:32,850 --> 00:05:33,940
You're nothing...

56
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:36,020
You're...

57
00:05:36,730 --> 00:05:38,110
What are you?

58
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,450
Did your family
treasure you too much?

59
00:05:45,450 --> 00:05:49,120
Yes. Ever since I was a child,
they'd express their love for me by...

60
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,290
As if!

61
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:52,120
That joke got old fast!

62
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:54,960
Damn you! Don't get cocky!

63
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:59,670
I don't show mercy to anyone
who messes with these animals!

64
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:02,970
Oh? You wanna fight me?

65
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:06,800
I commend your bravery, but don't
go crying to me when you die!

66
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,190
Gotcha!

67
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:19,730
Blast you!

68
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:24,990
Ranged weapons are cheating!

69
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:27,660
Then what about this thing here?!

70
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:29,490
Stop being selfish!

71
00:06:29,490 --> 00:06:30,620
Say your prayers!

72
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:49,430
Part-Part Quick Escape!

73
00:06:49,890 --> 00:06:51,350
Ow!

74
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:57,190
How dare you?! Blast it! Ow!

75
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:57,190
How dare I what?! Huh?!

76
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:10,830
Anyone who messes
with the animals has to pay!

77
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:15,410
You came to this island
to go after these creatures!

78
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:17,170
Why would I do that?!

79
00:07:17,170 --> 00:07:19,380
I didn't even want to come here!

80
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:23,300
You mean you're not a poacher?

81
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:38,560
What do you think? Good, huh?!

82
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,860
It's my very own cloudy sake!

83
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:42,980
Yeah, this is the best!

84
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:45,490
I can't remember
the last time I had a drink…

85
00:07:45,490 --> 00:07:49,740
You can have as many refills
as you want! Drink up!

86
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:52,830
And I'm really sorry about earlier!

87
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,500
That was some horrible stuff you did,

88
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,670
but it's water under the bridge!

89
00:07:57,670 --> 00:07:59,040
– Cheers!
– Cheers!

90
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:13,600
Sorry for asking you
to help make a raft, too.

91
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:16,730
Not at all. It was my pleasure.

92
00:08:17,730 --> 00:08:20,060
Okay! Take care of yourself!

93
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,400
You too!

94
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:36,290
Farewell, friend!

95
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,120
Take care!

96
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,840
Yeah...

97
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,800
You too!

98
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,880
Set sail!

99
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:55,720
Alright!

100
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:58,230
Buggy...

101
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:03,150
There are many strange
things in these waters.

102
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:07,110
Stay extra safe on your journey!

103
00:09:11,070 --> 00:09:13,910
Wait, I forgot to tell him about that!

104
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:25,880
Get a move on, Buggy!

105
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,590
Look out!

106
00:09:29,590 --> 00:09:32,590
Go! Get out of there!

107
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:38,060
What's that?

108
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:02,870
Pretty...

109
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,670
Who's that?

110
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,710
What a babe!

111
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:12,760
Well, at least he seems to be saved!

112
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,930
He had me sweating bullets there!

113
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:26,480
But anyway, take care of yourself!

114
00:10:26,770 --> 00:10:29,650
Thanks for the help!

115
00:10:29,650 --> 00:10:32,190
I flashily thought I was a goner there!

116
00:10:32,190 --> 00:10:34,070
There's no need for thanks.

117
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,950
You're Buggy the Clown, right?

118
00:10:37,490 --> 00:10:39,120
H-How do you know that?!

119
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,290
Who are you?

120
00:10:41,290 --> 00:10:44,040
I'm looking for a certain man.

121
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,750
I believe you're acquainted?

122
00:10:47,710 --> 00:10:49,040
That damn rubber brat!

123
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,380
Curse you!

124
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:52,880
Someday, I'll settle
the score with you!

125
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:54,680
Just you wait!

126
00:10:56,010 --> 00:10:58,010
This is the guy you're looking for?

127
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,640
I see.

128
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:05,440
So that's why you helped me.

129
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,770
Well, what do you say?

130
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,860
Will you team up with me?

131
00:11:12,690 --> 00:11:13,820
Sure, why not?

132
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:15,820
We both have the same goal.

133
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:17,740
Let's play ball.

134
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:20,580
That's great. Then cheers!

135
00:11:21,490 --> 00:11:22,620
Cheers!

136
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,590
Captain Buggy!

137
00:11:37,590 --> 00:11:42,680
When he was alive, I often felt
he was a ruthless and scary captain,

138
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:48,020
but now I realize he was a bold,
open-hearted, pirate's pirate!

139
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:51,520
Looking back, we were allowed
to pillage to our hearts' content

140
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:54,650
only because we had
Captain Buggy's support!

141
00:11:55,190 --> 00:12:01,120
Today, let's hold the greatest,
flashiest funeral for Captain Buggy!

142
00:12:03,330 --> 00:12:06,160
Captain, rest in peace!

143
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:09,670
Please leave everything to me,
Cabaji the Acrobat,

144
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:12,960
first officer of the Buggy Pirates!

145
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:17,420
I promise to rebuild the Buggy Pirates!

146
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:19,050
Hold it!

147
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,970
Cabaji!

148
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:21,970
What?!

149
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:27,810
It's only natural for Captain Buggy's
successor to be me,

150
00:12:27,810 --> 00:12:32,360
the first mate and amazing
Beast Tamer Mohji!

151
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:35,320
I'm the captain!

152
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,440
Hey, guys!

153
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:40,280
We're gonna test our strength
to see who will be captain!

154
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:43,370
Fine by me!

155
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:52,880
– Mohji! Mohji! Mohji!
– Mohji! Mohji! Mohji!

156
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:56,630
– Cabaji! Cabaji! Cabaji!
– Cabaji! Cabaji! Cabaji!

157
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,590
– Mohji! Mohji!
– Mohji! Mohji!

158
00:12:58,590 --> 00:13:00,470
– Cabaji! Cabaji!
– Cabaji! Cabaji!

159
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:02,590
– Mohji! Mohji!
– Mohji! Mohji!

160
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:04,470
– Cabaji! Cabaji!
– Cabaji! Cabaji!

161
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:06,930
– Mohji! Mohji!
– Mohji! Mohji!

162
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:27,870
Looks like I'll just have to fight you
until your body falls apart!

163
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:30,500
Yeah, let's duke it out mano a mano.

164
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:32,830
I'll take you down with my bare hands!

165
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:50,850
Damn you... J-Just give up already.

166
00:13:50,850 --> 00:13:54,150
N-No, you give up already.

167
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:20,670
– Yes! Our Captain Richie!
– Yes! Our Captain Richie!

168
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:52,830
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

169
00:14:52,830 --> 00:14:54,960
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

170
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:57,420
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

171
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:59,670
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

172
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:00,420
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

173
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:01,630
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

174
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:03,800
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

175
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,580
With Captain Buggy now gone,

176
00:14:56,580 --> 00:15:00,420
the most worthy of us
to be captain is Captain Richie!

177
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,880
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

178
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,600
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

179
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,560
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

180
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:12,850
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

181
00:15:12,850 --> 00:15:14,560
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

182
00:15:15,100 --> 00:15:17,230
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

183
00:15:17,230 --> 00:15:19,440
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

184
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,690
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

185
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:23,860
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!
– Captain Richie! Captain Richie!

186
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:26,280
– Our great captain!
– Our great captain!

187
00:15:41,090 --> 00:15:45,800
You do realize this island belongs
to us, the Bear Paw Tribe, right?!

188
00:15:47,430 --> 00:15:48,430
Captain!

189
00:15:53,890 --> 00:15:56,060
How amusing.
Are you picking a fight?!

190
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,660
W-We surrender.

191
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,840
Did you find something good?

192
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,800
Yeah! That's...

193
00:16:27,470 --> 00:16:31,930
the Buggy Pirates'
super flashy pirate ship!

194
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:36,350
But who did this? What bad luck!

195
00:16:36,930 --> 00:16:40,480
Not to mention this is
an old wanted poster.

196
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:43,860
Oh? There's someone
on the ground there.

197
00:16:44,900 --> 00:16:46,150
Wha...?!

198
00:16:46,610 --> 00:16:49,030
Mohji! Cabaji!

199
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:50,610
What happened to you guys?!

200
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:54,580
C-Captain Buggy...

201
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:58,540
I-It's so good to see you.

202
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:02,500
I'm so glad you're alive!

203
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:04,920
I thought we'd never see you again!

204
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:07,550
I-I'm so happy, too!

205
00:17:09,010 --> 00:17:13,100
But what the hell happened here?

206
00:17:14,220 --> 00:17:16,010
Who did this to you?!

207
00:17:16,010 --> 00:17:17,270
Huh?

208
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:20,770
We were punched out of the blue.

209
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:25,070
It's embarrassing, but we
can't remember a thing.

210
00:17:25,820 --> 00:17:29,740
The Bear Paw Tribe did this.

211
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:32,910
If you're going to save them,
you'd better hurry.

212
00:17:34,870 --> 00:17:38,250
Bear Paw tribesmen are famous
for their discerning palates.

213
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:55,050
The captain says that lions taste bad!

214
00:17:55,050 --> 00:17:56,970
We taste bad too!

215
00:17:56,970 --> 00:17:58,720
I won't make a good meal at all!

216
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:01,440
This guy looks better to eat than me!

217
00:18:00,230 --> 00:18:01,440
Lies! Lies!

218
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,270
He tastes much better!

219
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:06,570
I'm all bones! There's
hardly any meat on me!

220
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:10,280
Don't worry!

221
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:13,280
We're the Bear Paw Tribe!
That makes us iron chefs!

222
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:15,740
Some wine and spices
will take your smell away!

223
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:22,620
What do we do with this food?

224
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,000
What are they?

225
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,210
I've never seen such
odd ingredients.

226
00:18:26,670 --> 00:18:28,170
Do we boil this with them?

227
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:31,010
I just hope it doesn't
upset my stomach.

228
00:18:31,010 --> 00:18:32,470
Part-Part-Part...

229
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:39,010
Part-Part-Part-Part...

230
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,090
Is that...?!

231
00:19:10,670 --> 00:19:12,960
...Flashily Reassemble!

232
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:44,500
I'm back!

233
00:19:45,370 --> 00:19:49,380
– Captain Buggy!
– Captain Buggy!

234
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:54,090
Sorry I took so long, men!

235
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:59,430
Time to liven things up
with a super flashy Buggy Ball!

236
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:10,520
Richie!

237
00:20:18,950 --> 00:20:22,870
Acrobatics: Steamy Hot Spring
Murder Mystery!

238
00:20:22,870 --> 00:20:26,120
Let the beast-taming show begin!

239
00:20:33,250 --> 00:20:37,590
Do you really think you can hit me,
the great Buggy the Clown?!

240
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:44,390
I have to thank you all
for everything you did to my men!

241
00:20:45,020 --> 00:20:47,430
Here I flashily come!

242
00:20:48,810 --> 00:20:50,900
Part-Part Kick!

243
00:20:56,530 --> 00:20:58,860
Part-Part Punch!

244
00:21:00,700 --> 00:21:02,620
That's our captain!

245
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:11,290
– Captain Buggy!
– Captain Buggy!

246
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:15,670
I'm so glad you're safe!

247
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:20,630
I've caused you all such pain,
my dear underlings!

248
00:21:21,010 --> 00:21:24,970
Our pain is nothing at all!

249
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:34,440
All the hardships you've had
were because of...

250
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:36,690
that damn Straw Hat!

251
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:41,660
By the way, who is
this lovely, young lady?

252
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:46,330
This nice woman saved
my life! Her name is...

253
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,370
Uh...

254
00:21:48,370 --> 00:21:50,330
Um, I'm sorry.

255
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:52,540
What was your name again?

256
00:21:55,290 --> 00:21:56,670
Everyone!

257
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:59,800
The Buggy Pirates are back in action!

258
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:05,510
Captain! What should we do first?

259
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:09,930
Get the head of Monkey D. Luffy!

260
